Its just annoying having to always come into contact with people that think this. Locks are alot to maintain as with any hairstyle, surprisingly enough you can ACTUALLY keep them clean. Again i can not speak for everyone and I get it, as humans we like to fill in gaps on things we do not know. I honestly dont care how many videos you've watched of loc removal but luckily not everyone is the same kassie. I can say i would think people with straight hair would stink because their hair is greasy. Just slight ignorant comments like that can get to me and I apologize for being rude. Ive always enjoyed your videos and will still be a fan of you. Just dont keep pushing stereotypes, this message is for everyone. Thank you.
